nt could have locked an entire wedding party in undead suffering.  Suddenly, an unholy voice fills the air!  <br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Thrads shouts, in Human Tongue, &quot;*The voice fills the air once more, ringing in your head*  The site of unholy matrimony ... T'Serinna did slay them in her rage against Mayong ... *the voice fades off into silence*</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Maladominus says, in Dark Elvish, 'more voices in my head.  Make it stop!'<br>
Juonar says, in Dark Elvish, 'omg'<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Didi shouts, in Dark Elvish, '*this has been a scheduled test of your unholy voices, if this had been a real unholy voice you would have been asked to evacuate the building.  Please report in to your local unholy voice warden.  End of message.'</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Maladominus laughs at Didi.<br>
Didi snickers softly.<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE BOLD START--><b> Thrads shouts, in Human Tongue, 'Please evacuate the zone.'</b><!--EZCODE BOLD END--><br>
<br>
Opious says, in Dark Elvish, 'we're so dead'<br>
Spartax tells the group, in Dark Elvish, 'lol'<br>
Bellenae shouts, in Dark Elvish, '/panic'<br>
